channel.title: Why does PI have memory leaks?
channel.description: I've been wondering this, and I notice it just about every time I try to do something on my server... if I can't fix it I might just all together move to hyperion or something... (Don't really like/enjoy delta at all ;p) But if anyone could explain this that'd be nice.

item.title: Why does PI have memory leaks?
item.dc:creator: @RiiPiiNFtW RiiPiiNFtW
item.description:
@RiiPiiNFtW wrote:

One day Sanity tried to be kewl by inventing a new base. He succeeded. He failed in his conventions though. He coded through notpad which made the code a lot more messy.

Lesson learned, use an IDE. -.-’
